GreywoodwoodnM0none066843635searchvar1.17112*******An old village, recently deserted, lies in its center, testifying of the consequences of war. Frightened by an eventual raid by the Topazian forces, so far away from the protection of Diamond's army, greywood occupants ran away, leaving a beautiful, resourceful wood for the enemy to take easily. At least, these woods might be exempted from bloodbathes.